title: I have not got my 10th birthday stuff
body: I haven't gotten riot kayle or the poro birthday hat, and I've played games, so can someone help me?

replies.body: As *Zombiemaster* mentioned, we're still getting these gifts sent out until the 30th. We're sending these out in batches to confirm they get out properly, so let me know if you don't have anything after the 30th.

The gifts are still being distributed as per the banner on the [support page](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us). Due to how the gifts are being given out, the final date to receive them has been moved back to the 30th.
